ActFarm Products Agencies Act
SubjectCanadian Beef Cattle Research Market Development and Promotion Agency ** AMENDMENT TO PROCLAMATION **
PrecisOrder amending the CANADIAN BEEF CATTLE RESEARCH MARKET DEVELOPMENT AND PROMOTION AGENCY PROCLAMATION by removing the eligibility requirements, ensuring that the terms of the Agency's proclamation correspond to subsection 40(1)(e) of the Farm Products Agencies Act.
